{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/animationName\"><code>animationName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>elapsedTime</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/pseudoElement\"><code>pseudoElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>AnimationEvent.elapsedTime</strong></code> は読み取り専用のプロパティで、アニメーションが開始されてからの秒数を <code>float</code> 型で表します。このイベントが発生したとき、アニメーションが停止した場合を除いて常に設定されます。 <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/animationstart_event\" title=\"animationstart\"><code>animationstart</code></a> イベントにおいては <code>elapsedTime</code> は <code>0.0</code> になりますが、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\"><code>animation-delay</code></a> が負の値の場合は、このイベントは <code>elapsedTime</code> が <code>(-1 * </code><em>待ち時間</em><code>)</code> であるときに発生します。.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">time = <em>AnimationEvent</em>.elapsedTime</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-animations-1/#dom-animationevent-elapsedtime\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Animations Level 1<br><small lang=\"ja\">AnimationEvent.elapsedTime の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Animations/Using_CSS_animations\">CSS アニメーションの使用</a></li>\n <li>アニメーションに関する CSS プロパティと @ 規則: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation\"><code>animation</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\"><code>animation-delay</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-direction\"><code>animation-direction</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-duration\"><code>animation-duration</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-fill-mode\"><code>animation-fill-mode</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-iteration-count\"><code>animation-iteration-count</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-name\"><code>animation-name</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-play-state\"><code>animation-play-state</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/animation-timing-function\"><code>animation-timing-function</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/@keyframes\"><code>@keyframes</code></a>.</li>\n <li>所属先の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a> インターフェイス</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime は読み取り専用のプロパティで、アニメーションが開始されてからの秒数を float 型で表します。このイベントが発生したとき、アニメーションが停止した場合を除いて常に設定されます。 animationstart イベントにおいては elapsedTime は 0.0 になりますが、 animation-delay が負の値の場合は、このイベントは elapsedTime が (-1 * 待ち時間) であるときに発生します。.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/animationevent/elapsedtime","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/animationevent/elapsedtime/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent","title":"AnimationEvent"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime","title":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime"}],"pageTitle":"AnimationEvent.elapsedTime - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}